Information
------------------------------

Expedition Unknown Series 2: Searching for Shangri-La
Josh ventures into Nepal to investigate the mythical paradise of Shangri-La.
Shangri La is a utopian valley hidden somewhere in the Himalayas. Legend says it's a paradise on Earth where people find immortality. Josh Gates climbs into the mountains of Nepal to investigate mysterious "sky caves" hundreds of feet above the ground that may provide clues to a real life Shangri La.
